::{{A|VO chapter3 18 welt 109 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter3 18 welt 109 f.ogg}} '''Welt:''' You're still carrying the keepsake the IPC envoy gave you, right, (Trailblazer)? May I borrow it for a moment?
